"StackTach is a tool created by Rackspace to collect and report the "
"notifications sent by <code>nova</code>. Notifications are essentially the "
"same as logs, but can be much more detailed. A good overview of "
"notifications can be found at <link title=\"StackTach GitHub repo\" href="
"\"https://wiki.openstack.org/wiki/SystemUsageData\">System Usage Data</link> "
